room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
room_description: It's a dark and dingy night and your car has just broken down. The only thing you can see for miles around is a motel. Upon entering you notice that you are the only person in there. When you try to leave, you realize that the door has been locked from the outside. You will have to figure out how to escape this crazy motel within an hour or less to be successful before the person who locked you in returns.
